## 11.17 A worked audit

```scheme
(define (audit-runtime)
  (let ((all (snapshot-registry)))
    (list
      :total-verbs (length all)
      :by-namespace (group-by-namespace all)
      :by-perm (group-by-perm all)
      :by-tier (group-by-tier all)
      :undocumented (count-undocumented all)
      :deprecated (count-deprecated all))))
```

One function that reports on the whole language surface. The primitives compose.

## 11.18 A worked report

```scheme
(audit-runtime)
;; => (:total-verbs 512
;;     :by-namespace ((base . 87) (list . 34) (string . 22) (cortex . 6) (composer . 15) ...)
;;     :by-perm ((read . 380) (paint . 52) (animate . 8) (state-change . 45) (financial . 3) ...)
;;     :by-tier ((core . 335) (extended . 155) (experimental . 22))
;;     :undocumented 13
;;     :deprecated 6)
```

That is a snapshot of Motoi's language surface. 512 verbs. Most are read. 335 are frozen core. 13 need docs. Actionable, from the introspection primitives.

